snippet.title: Egg Time (VR game) release trailer
snippet.description:
Egg Time (VR game)
Available on Steam for free : http://store.steampowered.com/app/531990

Crazy game for Virtual reality, it is a first atempt of TEDI Games studio to create a VR game, currently in ALPHA stage where the basic functionality is tested.

The game revolves around simple mechanics and physics.

Attributions:
Music : Fun in a Bottle Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
